		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div data-pf-type="Body" class="sc-pRgDJ fzXWJx pf-8e55ee00"><div data-pf-type="Layout" class="pf-1eb7703d"><div data-container="false" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-5c094f86" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-b7703dd6 pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--2 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--4"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-703dd614" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--9 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--5"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-3dd614e4" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-5488a24d"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-14e47b7e">FAQs&nbsp;<br></span></h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-4cee1cc2"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-7b7e4c86">GENERAL</span></h3><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC GftoS pf-7e4c86f8"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-4c86f801 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-98c6b981 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="c2dc98c6-b981-4813-9148-c42a87f17dc0" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="true" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>1. Why True Sons hair dye products?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-48c42a87 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="c2dc98c6-b981-4813-9148-c42a87f17dc0" style="display: block;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-f8011b55"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-d148c42a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-1b558858">True Sons was developed to give guys a higher-quality alternative to cheap drugstore brands. Our innovative, patent-pending foam formula can be applied with or without mixing to achieve a subtle effect that looks natural, not fake. If you are a dye virgin, or just hate the shoe-polish look, then True Sons might be for you.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-5588584f accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-f17dc046 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="2a87f17d-c046-4b61-b8c9-1b7f42907863" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>2. Where can I try True Sons?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-c91b7f42 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="2a87f17d-c046-4b61-b8c9-1b7f42907863" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-584f54a6"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-78c91b7f"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-54a68f38">True Sons is available online via TrueSons.com website and on Amazon.com. It can be delivered to your door bi-monthly or semi-annual basis in a cool, discreet packaging.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-a68f38d3 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-9078631b accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="7f429078-631b-42cc-8c5a-26c07e8c7e6c" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>3. How long does each bottle last?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-5a26c07e accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="7f429078-631b-42cc-8c5a-26c07e8c7e6c" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-38d3fbd8"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-0c5a26c0"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-fbd88022">True Sons is an aerosol. That means it can be reused for multiple applications over a long period of time. How much you need depends on the length of your hair and how many body parts you are dyeing. Everyone is different.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d8802243 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-8c7e6c95 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="c07e8c7e-6c95-4c55-950f-47bfc38c529a" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>4. How many applications can I get from one bottle?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-0f47bfc3 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="c07e8c7e-6c95-4c55-950f-47bfc38c529a" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-224312b9"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-550f47bf"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-12b96c2b">One bottle of True Sons is good for 3-4 applications for the average user.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-b96c2b2e accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-8c529a54 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="bfc38c52-9a54-4a80-8d5f-0be14a84b313" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>5. How is it different from other men’s hair dyes?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-5f0be14a accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="bfc38c52-9a54-4a80-8d5f-0be14a84b313" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-2b2e9e8e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-cd5f0be1"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-9e8e9745">True Sons Hair Dye Foam is the first foam hair dye available in the USA for men. It’s contains oxidative dye which react when they come in contact with the air. That means it works without the addition of developer to give guys results that look gradual and natural. It can also be mixed with True Sons Dye Booster, a 20 volume cream developer, for more grey coverage.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-8e974596 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-84b3138d accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e14a84b3-138d-4d89-b526-8b8117852000" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>6. How easy is the application process?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-268b8117 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e14a84b3-138d-4d89-b526-8b8117852000" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-4596beea"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-b5268b81"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-beeab4bc">It’s easier than shaving. And no nicks. <a style="text-decoration: underline" href="https://truesons.com/pages/how-to-dye">Click here</a> to see a full explanation of the application process.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-eab4bcb0 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-85200031 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="81178520-0031-4e97-b0f3-e91e23a29fb7" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>7. What parts of my body can I dye with True Sons?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-f3e91e23 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="81178520-0031-4e97-b0f3-e91e23a29fb7" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-bcb0c390"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-f0f3e91e"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-c390955a">You can use the same True Sons foam on multiple body parts including scalp (head) hair, beard hair, chest hair and arm hair. However, True Sons cannot ever be used on your eyebrows or eyelashes. Getting dye in your eyes is extremely dangerous. Please be careful. We also have never tested True Sons on the pubic area so please don’t use it near your business district. You might give a whole new meaning to the term ‘blue balls’.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-90955a4d accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-a29fb756 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="1e23a29f-b756-4656-879e-740a8b60ca76" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>8. Will True Sons stain my skin?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-9e740a8b accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="1e23a29f-b756-4656-879e-740a8b60ca76" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-5a4d60ab"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-879e740a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-60ab6a83">As with all hair dyes, there are risks of temporary staining to your skin. Read the User’s Guide attached to your monthly box to learn how to minimize staining. Again, using on the pubic area is NOT RECOMMENDED for this reason and others.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-ab6a83aa accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-60ca7681 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="0a8b60ca-7681-423e-bceb-327a82cb1fed" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>9. Will it stain my sink and towels?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-eb327a82 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="0a8b60ca-7681-423e-bceb-327a82cb1fed" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-83aaf0fb"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-3ceb327a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f0fb33f8">Yes! It will stain everything unless it is cleaned up. For the sink (and even walls) of your bathroom, we recommend thoroughly wiping down all surfaces post application. And we mean everywhere, especially light colored. We recommend using cheap, dark-colored towels to towel off. Light colors will show stains immediately.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-fb33f88a accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-cb1fed3d accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="7a82cb1f-ed3d-447c-8309-b4fb16b7e161" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>10. Can True Sons be reused for multiple applications?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-09b4fb16 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="7a82cb1f-ed3d-447c-8309-b4fb16b7e161" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-f88ac04f"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-c309b4fb"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-c04ff0e3">Yes! You can reuse True Sons Hair Dye Foam for multiple applications. If applied weekly, each bottle should last about a month, depending your hair length and how many areas you dye. True Sons is packaged in a hermetically sealed aerosol can which protects the oxidative dyes from reacting until you are ready to dye again.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-4ff0e339 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-b7e16161 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="fb16b7e1-6161-4630-89cb-190b5fa59689" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>11. How long is the process?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-cb190b5f accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="fb16b7e1-6161-4630-89cb-190b5fa59689" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-e3394bb3"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-c9cb190b"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-4bb397de">We recommend applying the product for 15 minutes the first time and evaluating the results. Need more penetration? Reapply in 5-minute intervals until you reach your desired shade.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-b397de37 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-a5968966 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="0b5fa596-8966-4332-971b-86e556cfbeb7" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>12. When do I start timing?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-1b86e556 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="0b5fa596-8966-4332-971b-86e556cfbeb7" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-de37135e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-571b86e5"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-135eb3e4">Start counting the time after all dye foam (or mixture of dye + developer) is applied to the area. And dye one area at a time, please. Don’t be greedy.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-5eb3e41e accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-cfbeb7bc accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e556cfbe-b7bc-4d76-8571-562e063d4e3a" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>13. How often should I use True Sons?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-71562e06 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e556cfbe-b7bc-4d76-8571-562e063d4e3a" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-e41e770e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-0571562e"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-770ef6c3">That’s up to you, but we recommend reapplying once or twice a week at first. Using it more often may cause irritation. Each application should not exceed 25 minutes max.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-0ef6c3e9 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-3d4e3a70 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="2e063d4e-3a70-4f4e-9964-88ff9f9429d8" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>14. How often will I have to reorder?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-6488ff9f accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="2e063d4e-3a70-4f4e-9964-88ff9f9429d8" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-c3e98c6e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-196488ff"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-8c6ea4cc">Most guys use one can of True Sons Hair dye per month but everyone is different, based on the amount of grey, frequency of application and length of hair being treated. To get the best price, take advantage of our 6 cans in one shipment option. It saves trees for our planet and saves money for you!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-6ea4cc0b accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-9429d836 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="ff9f9429-d836-4519-b3d1-c2b8277bb2c9" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>15. Do I really have to do a patch test 48 hours ahead of time?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-d1c2b827 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="ff9f9429-d836-4519-b3d1-c2b8277bb2c9" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-cc0bd6a6"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-33d1c2b8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d6a65e02">Yes, you really do. Allergic reactions are rare but they do happen. How many years did you wait to try dyeing? 48 more hours won’t make a difference. You have been warned!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-a65e0253 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-7bb2c9db accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="b8277bb2-c9db-48f7-be7a-64b182b45234" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>16. Should I wash my hair before applying True Sons foam?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-7a64b182 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="b8277bb2-c9db-48f7-be7a-64b182b45234" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-02537077"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-fe7a64b1"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-70773f82">Sure. But your hair should be dry when applying True Sons and you should rinse off thoroughly immediately after dyeing. Dye on your hair will continue to react for up to 24 hours post application. This means it may look a bit darker 1-2 days after application.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-773f82f5 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-b45234eb accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="b182b452-34eb-46db-9934-f3307096d5e2" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>17. Should I shampoo after dyeing?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-34f33070 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="b182b452-34eb-46db-9934-f3307096d5e2" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-82f5e9c2"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-9934f330"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-e9c25c59">You can if you want but it is not required. Simple rinse with water until the water runs clear. Every time you shampoo your hair, you remove some of the dye. The more shampoos, the quicker you will need to reapply.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-c25c5943 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-96d5e234 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="307096d5-e234-4464-9f09-8eb54825a2b5" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>18. Are color-extending shampoos okay to use?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-098eb548 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="307096d5-e234-4464-9f09-8eb54825a2b5" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-5943003c"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-1f098eb5"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-003c6ce6">Yes, color-extending shampoos are fine to use. They may help extend the length of time between applications. </span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-3c6ce6d3 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-25a2b5f0 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="b54825a2-b5f0-4fc7-8a95-107750e8033f" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>19. What are these wipes anyway?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-95107750 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="b54825a2-b5f0-4fc7-8a95-107750e8033f" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-e6d3459a"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-0a951077"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-459a76f6">The wipes are specially formulated to remove stains from skin. It’s normal to see some staining. This usually goes away after a day. To reduce the risk of staining, remove any foam that gets on the hairline during application to prevent exposure. Some guys also choose to line their beard or hair line with Vaseline or Chapstick to create an impenetrable barrier that protects the exposed skin from the dye. </span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-9a76f69c accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-e8033f2b accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="7750e803-3f2b-421d-9581-c69986a4197a" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>20. I used to dye my hair with a drugstore brand. How can I match that shade?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-81c69986 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="7750e803-3f2b-421d-9581-c69986a4197a" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-f69c716e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-9581c699"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-716e92d5">Click here for a chart that we created to help steer you right. When we developed our line of shades, we purchased every single shade offered by some of our competitors. Even we couldn’t tell the difference between some of them, the results were so subtle. We decided that our shade line is all you really need to get good results. </span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-6e92d543 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-a4197a81 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="9986a419-7a81-4d04-b4f5-974401f230c4" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>21. How do I find my perfect shade?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-f5974401 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="9986a419-7a81-4d04-b4f5-974401f230c4" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-d543eb9f"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-34f59744"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-eb9fa4be">Ask your barber, partner or a close friend you trust to not give away your secret! Then try one of our shades. If it’s not right, then you can edit your shade choice at least one week before your next shipment. </span></p></div></div></div></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-f230c438"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-a4becb6c">ORDERING QUESTIONS</span></h3><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC GftoS pf-becb6c9e"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-cb6c9e3d accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-39754b6d accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="38453975-4b6d-4ecf-b7a0-ca93da4fd542" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>1. Can I change my shade whenever I want? </button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-a0ca93da accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="38453975-4b6d-4ecf-b7a0-ca93da4fd542" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-9e3d32c6"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-37a0ca93"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-32c6d68f">You can change the shade you receive for each shipment by changing your account settings one week before your next ship date.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-c6d68f52 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-4fd54222 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="93da4fd5-4222-4103-a6a6-51e46422c581" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>2. Can I change the frequency whenever I want?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-a651e464 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="93da4fd5-4222-4103-a6a6-51e46422c581" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-8f52ecd0"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-26a651e4"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-ecd074a4">You can choose between bi-monthly or semi-annual shipments of True Sons. To change your delivery frequency, log into your account.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d074a409 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-22c58144 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e46422c5-8144-4e44-9364-95104af11a75" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>3. Can I cancel or edit frequency whenever I want?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-6495104a accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e46422c5-8144-4e44-9364-95104af11a75" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-a4099811"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-53649510"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-98113581">Yes. Any plan changes, including cancellations, must be received one full week before your next shipment date. You can also pause or skip a shipment by logging into your account, going to Manage Subscription, click ORDER # and adjust each shipment to your liking.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-1135811a accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-f11a7590 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="104af11a-7590-4d80-8c6b-ba2c7087eef4" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>4. How do I cancel?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-6bba2c70 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="104af11a-7590-4d80-8c6b-ba2c7087eef4" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-811a00dd"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-0c6bba2c"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-00dd3b7d">To cancel your subscription, send us a request here: https://truesons.com/pages/contact Any plan changes, including cancellations, must be received one full week before your next shipment date.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-dd3b7dc0 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-87eef45c accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="2c7087ee-f45c-4751-a91c-1f2b6b3f03f2" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>5. How long will it take my order to arrive?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-1c1f2b6b accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="2c7087ee-f45c-4751-a91c-1f2b6b3f03f2" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-7dc05b85"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-691c1f2b"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-5b855c46">True Sons usually ships out new orders within 1 business day. It can take up to 5-7 business days to be delivered, as our aerosol cans contain pressurized gas that can only ship ground. We are not able to offer expedited, air, or international shipping at this time. We are able to ship to PO and APO boxes.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-855c4687 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-3f03f2ad accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="2b6b3f03-f2ad-45b6-aab1-1305a016267f" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>6. Where do you ship?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-b11305a0 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="2b6b3f03-f2ad-45b6-aab1-1305a016267f" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-46872f80"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-6ab11305"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-2f807081">We currently ship only within the continental United States only. Sorry, Hawaii, Alaska, and Guam!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-8070819e accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-16267f42 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="05a01626-7f42-4634-b347-b567dc0a8c61" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>7. Can I make a one time purchase?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-47b567dc accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="05a01626-7f42-4634-b347-b567dc0a8c61" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-819ee2ce"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-f347b567"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-e2cee225">True Sons is available in limited quantities, so we can only make it available to people who subscribe. However, if you aren’t completely happy with your purchase, you can cancel at least one week before the next shipment. You can also or skip a shipment by logging into your account, going to Manage Subscription, click ORDER # and adjust each shipment as you wish.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-cee22531 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-0a8c6124 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="67dc0a8c-6124-4209-9164-42b95d388c86" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>8. Can I purchase True Sons at a retail location?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-6442b95d accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="67dc0a8c-6124-4209-9164-42b95d388c86" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-2531b73c"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-916442b9"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-b73c922a">Not yet. True Sons is only available online at TrueSons.com and Amazon.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-3c922ad3 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-388c8691 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="b95d388c-8691-4fa9-aabc-60c79be8c481" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>9. Can I return product?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-bc60c79b accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="b95d388c-8691-4fa9-aabc-60c79be8c481" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-2ad35d18"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-aabc60c7"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-5d18efd8">True Sons does not offer refunds for any reason. We will happily exchange unopened and unused bottles for a different shade.</span></p></div></div></div></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-e8c481af"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-efd81a3f">PRODUCT SPECIFIC</span></h3><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC GftoS pf-53c15c09"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d81a3fed accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-d6dd015b accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="afffd6dd-015b-4d81-b7e3-77e9bb254051" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>1. Can women use True Sons products?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-e377e9bb accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="afffd6dd-015b-4d81-b7e3-77e9bb254051" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-3feda534"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-f7e377e9"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-a5347773">Of course! Although True Sons was made specifically for men, women can use our products as well to achieve a natural look. However, we are only available in a limited number of shades.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-347773b7 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-25405155 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e9bb2540-5155-428b-a7f4-3bb0ca8d8115" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>2. Where is it made?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-f43bb0ca accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e9bb2540-5155-428b-a7f4-3bb0ca8d8115" style="display: none;" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-73b7e50d"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-e7f43bb0"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-e50dcb62">We proudly manufacture and fill our product within the USA. Some ingredients and materials that go into the product are sourced outside the USA.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-0dcb62b3 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-8d81